---
// In practice -- say it, watch it happen.
---

<section class="section section--practice">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">in practice</p>
    <h2 class="section__title">say it. watch it happen.</h2>

    <ul class="practice">
      <li class="practice__row">
        <span class="practice__what">Build entire networks from a sentence</span>
        <span class="practice__say">"Build me a noise-driven particle system."</span>
      </li>
      <li class="practice__row">
        <span class="practice__what">Try a different approach in seconds</span>
        <span class="practice__say">"Actually, make it react to audio instead."</span>
      </li>
      <li class="practice__row">
        <span class="practice__what">Set any parameter</span>
        <span class="practice__say">"Set the noise frequency to match the audio input."</span>
      </li>
      <li class="practice__row">
        <span class="practice__what">Write extensions</span>
        <span class="practice__say">"Create an extension class that manages scene transitions."</span>
      </li>
      <li class="practice__row">
        <span class="practice__what">Debug errors</span>
        <span class="practice__say">"Why is my render chain producing a black output?"</span>
      </li>
      <li class="practice__row">
        <span class="practice__what">Compare attempts</span>
        <span class="practice__say">"Show me what changed between this version and the last."</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
